========================================
FENRIR "NO!"
========================================

Name: Fenrir
Surname: "No!" (as repeatedly called by his former owner)
Full Name: Fenrir "No!"

Race: Custom Lineage (Awakened Chihuahua – flavor only)
Class: Warlock 1 (The Celestial)
Background: Former Pet (Custom Background)
Alignment: Neutral (leaning Good)

Gender: Male
Age: 1 year
Size: Small (Chihuahua – flavor)
Speed: 25 ft


========================================
APPEARANCE / RP
========================================

A small, long-haired brown Chihuahua with an oversized sense of importance.
Fenrir stands proudly, chest forward, alert to every movement in the world.
He believes himself to be a chosen champion of the heavens.

He does not question this belief.

(All description is flavor only; no mechanical effects)


